    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine is currently underperforming and requires a major overhaul to be roadworthy, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping and delayed engagement. Externally, the body shows signs of heavy wear, including several deep scratches, minor dents, and areas of rust that will need treatment. The interior has also seen better days, with visible tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronic components. This car is ideal for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a comprehensive restoration project or for someone in need of a donor vehicle for spare parts.",
