    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels wonderful on the road. It runs smoothly, has plenty of life left, and is ready for its next big adventure today! Feel free to message me if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
