    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a mechanically sound example of the E46 platform, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining the car\u2019s signature 50/50 weight distribution and high-speed stability. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving internals are operating at peak efficiency. A driver-focused machine with excellent mechanical feedback.",
