    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience the perfect blend of performance and luxury with this impeccably maintained 2018 Porsche Cayenne. Finished in a stunning Midnight Blue Metallic, the exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front valence reflect its honest road use. Inside, the Luxor Beige leather interior remains supple and clean; while there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster consistent with careful use, the cabin is strictly non-smoker and all electronics, from the navigation to the panoramic sunroof, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is exceptionally sound, benefiting from a documented service history at authorized centers. It recently received a fresh set of premium all-season tires and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The 3.0L V6 engine delivers smooth, responsive power through the 8-speed Tiptronic transmission, providing a confident and quiet ride. This is a dependable, well-cared-for example that presents beautifully and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
